_70 for the NSIS profile and C=7.6+-0.5 and\nr_200=2.55+-0.07 Mpc/h_70 for the NFW profile. Using the same image\nconfiguration as Broadhurst et al. 2005 we obtain a strong lensing model that\nis superior to that of Broadhurst et al. 2005 (rms of 2.7'' compared to 3.2'').\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 May 2006 09:32:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
