rs that were born and died before the\nUniverse was ten per cent of its current age, so GRB afterglow reverberations\nprovide clues about the environments around some of the first stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 May 2006 20:40:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
